QuestData.Title: Buzzers for Baby
QuestData.Description: <The tiny seedling opens its leaves wide, like a baby bird waiting to be fed. It speaks in a very faint voice:>$B$BHungry... want... bugs...<You can hear the buzzing of wasps to the south. Could they be what the little thing wants to feed on?>
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 10 Ironwood Buzzers to feed the Seedling Protector.
QuestData.RewardText: <The seedling pats its stalk with a rooty arm, as if full. It looks to have grown a bit, too!>
